{"tid":985854,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"冬之上高地","createTime":"2019-01-18T03:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T19:11:59.000Z","uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fef35b4a5961c12a697017b17dd39d30b71bbd3","tid":985854,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"有無巴打試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年冬天去 知道封山無得入<br />\n但竟然搵到有tour行山入<br />\n唔知正常人支唔支持到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AipvyM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AipvyM.png&h=5c9627f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"693338d5bcda31b333c324ce2da16f814350fbd4","tid":985854,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"幾年前去過，3月尾開始溶雪<br />\n高山有巴士去到中之湯隧道口，我係前一晚搭過去中之湯溫泉旅館住，巴士站附近可以接送（好撚正，淡季無人住個溫泉包場咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，老闆好熱情，知道我地第二朝打算6點出發就前一晚食完晚餐比埋飯糰比我地做早餐，好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n行路穿過隧道（隧道入口側邊係行人路）經過大正池，河童橋，去到明神池做終點，返轉頭出返隧道搭尾班巴士出返高山（隧道口就係間旅館個接待小屋，呢個時候老闆已經幫我地送好晒行李過去）<br />\n<br />\n全程由出發到返到小屋係咁停低影相大約12粒鐘，全平路，沿途見到有日本人帶小朋友一齊行，所以其實唔難，都有日本人紮營過夜，我地第一次行雪地咩都唔識就咁一對防水行山boot去行，但建議都係買返雪抓安全好多"},{"pid":"e1bd0b8ee0b49530a3043842b826cb270670c36d","tid":985854,"uid":230511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"附圖幾張，冬天去真係好撚靚！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d55Wnmd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd55Wnmd.png&h=4ca8970a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKe8dsY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKe8dsY.png&h=66c7dbfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G698ds1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG698ds1.png&h=e8a77d30&s={SIZE}\" /><img 